          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>Ahead of Red Dead Redemption's Nintendo Switch 2 update next month, Amazon is offering a discount on the recently rereleased physical edition for Switch. Rockstar Games distributed a new budget-friendly $30 edition in September, and now you can <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FPRNCXKB?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">grab a copy of Red Dead Redemption for $25</a> during <a href="https://amzn.to/4nUYU6z" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Amazon's early Black Friday video game sale</a>. </p><p>Red Dead Redemption's physical edition for Switch includes the full game and Undead Nightmare expansion on the cartridge. The <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/red-dead-redemption-rated-for-switch-2-ps5-and-xbox-series-x-s/1100-6536175/" data-ref-id="1100-6536175">Switch 2 update</a> will be available December 2, and it's free for owners of the Switch edition. The digital version still retails for $50, so you can save 50% by picking up the physical edition instead. Amazon's early <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/black-friday/">Black Friday sale</a> also includes the Switch port of <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/grand-theft-auto-trilogy-nintendo-switch-amazon-game-deal-black-friday-2025/1100-6533883/" data-ref-id="1100-6533883">Grand Theft Auto: The Trilogy - The Definitive Edition</a> for $20 (was $30).</p><div title="6534660 - Red Dead Redemption and GTA Trilogy for Switch" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="4321" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="6534660 - Red Dead Redemption and GTA Trilogy for Switch" data-collection="">                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FPRNCXKB?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B0FPRNCXKB?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FPRNCXKB?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20">Red Dead Redemption for Nintendo Switch</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FPRNCXKB?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B0FPRNCXKB?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FPRNCXKB?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20">$25 (was $30)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>Red Dead Redemption's Switch 2 update will offer 60fps as well as enhanced visuals with HDR and DLSS. Switch 2 players will also be able to play Red Dead Redemption with Joy-Con 2 mouse controls.</p><p>If you're buying RDR to play on the original Switch, you should know it's still a pretty impressive port from a technical perspective. It runs at a stable 30fps in handheld and docked modes with 720p and 1080p resolution, respectively.</p><p>Red Dead Redemption is a spaghetti western that nails the mythic appeal of being a cowboy. The game doesn't stray far from the open-world template that Rockstar perfected with its previous GTA releases. You have the freedom to explore, cause trouble, and complete quests provided by the large cast of memorable characters.</p><p>John Marston's journey across the sprawling expanses of the American Wild West and Mexico to bury his blood-stained past and protect his family is a memorable one.</p><p>Along with the base game, this edition of RDR comes with Undead Nightmare, a horror-themed adventure in which the world around you has been transformed into an apocalyptic landscape overrun with zombies. Undead Nightmare was originally released as a standalone expansion, but these days it's bundled with the base game on modern platforms.</p></div>                      </div>                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Grand-Theft-Auto-Trilogy-Definitive-Nintendo/dp/B0FK6N3H12?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Grand-Theft-Auto-Trilogy-Definitive-Nintendo\/dp\/B0FK6N3H12?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Grand-Theft-Auto-Trilogy-Definitive-Nintendo/dp/B0FK6N3H12?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20">Grand Theft Auto: The Trilogy for Nintendo Switch</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Grand-Theft-Auto-Trilogy-Definitive-Nintendo/dp/B0FK6N3H12?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Grand-Theft-Auto-Trilogy-Definitive-Nintendo\/dp\/B0FK6N3H12?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Grand-Theft-Auto-Trilogy-Definitive-Nintendo/dp/B0FK6N3H12?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20">$20 (was $30)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>If you also want to explore the city streets of the modern age, check out Grand Theft Auto: The Trilogy - The Definitive Edition for only $20 (was $30). This collection still retails for $60 on the eShop, but Rockstar rereleased the physical version a few months back with a budget-friendly MSRP.</p><p>Grand Theft Auto: The Trilogy collects three PS2-era classics: GTA 3, Vice City, and San Andreas. The Definitive Edition launched in rough shape, but all three games are much better these days thanks to multiple patches and a significant overhaul last fall.</p><p>When you pop in the game card for the first time, you will be prompted to download roughly GTA: Vice City from the eShop (roughly 9GB). San Andreas and GTA III are stored on the card. The digital version of the trilogy from the eShop, for reference, is 25.4GB.</p></div>                      </div>   </div><h3>Nintendo Switch 1/2 Early Black Friday Deals at Amazon</h3><p>Along with deals on the pair of Rockstar Games titles, Amazon has deals on a bunch of other Switch and Switch 2 games. For more classics, check out <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/legacy-of-kain-soul-reaver-12-prime-day-2-sale/1100-6535221/" data-ref-id="1100-6535221">Legacy of Kain: Soul Reaver 1&amp;2 Remastered</a> and <a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1&amp;isPreview=1&amp;asins=B0F95MGBCZ,B0F95KSK4Q,B0F95XWM3Y,B0F95PGXH3,B0F95X313H,B0D4F9PJ4L,B0D4FCT4YG,B0D4FCT4C6,B0D4F9YN5X,B0D4F9Y7CW&amp;tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Tomb Raider IV-VI Remastered</a>, both of which have nice Deluxe Editions with collectibles for $35 or less.</p><ul><li><a href="https://amzn.to/4oKofBC" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">All Nintendo Switch 2 Deals</a></li><li><a href="https://amzn.to/4a2emKK" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">All Nintendo Switch Deals</a></li><li><a href="https://amzn.to/3K5Vm3y" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Nintendo Switch Game Deals</a></li><li><a href="https://amzn.to/4i06ETu" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Nintendo Switch 1/2 Controller Deals</a></li></ul><hr><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/meta-quest-3s-vr-headset-best-black-friday-deals/1100-6532962/">Meta Quest 3S Batman Bundle Is $70 Off, Comes With $50 Amazon Gift Card</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-gamecube-third-party-controller-switch-2-pc-amazon-holiday-deal/1100-6532458/">Grab A Wireless GameCube-Style Controller For Switch 1/2 &amp; PC For Only $40</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/lunar-remastered-collection-amazon-exclusive-physical-edition-deal-switch-playstation-xbox/1100-6528818/">Amazon-Exclusive Lunar Remastered Collection Gets First Price Cut</a></li>                          <li>         <span>+ Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals &amp; Preorders Links (5)</span>       </li>          <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/final-fantasy-magic-the-gathering-set-deals-restock-preorder-buying-guide/2900-6271/">Final Fantasy Magic: The Gathering Booster Box Restocked With Huge Discount At Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-hunger-games-sunrising-on-the-reaping-gift-edition-book-box-set-deals/1100-6535218/">Sunrise On The Reaping New Collector's Gift Edition Is Already Discounted At Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/lego-dc-batman-construction-figure-and-bat-pod-bike-the-dark-knight-amazon-deal/1100-6535073/">Lego DC Batman Figure &amp; Bat-Pod Is Over 50% Off At Amazon, Sold Out Everywhere Else</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/honkai-star-rail-8bitdo-ultimate-2-wireless-controller-collector-bundle-amazon-deal/1100-6534680/">Honkai: Star Rail 8BitDo Ultimate 2 Collector's Bundle Gets First Discount</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/best-xbox-elite-series-2-wireless-controller-deal-holiday-2025/1100-6535861/">Xbox Elite Series 2 Deal: Save $60 On Microsoft's Premium Wireless Controller</a></li>   </ul> </div>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
